data.description: Enchanting Riverside Retreat at an Unmatched Price – Now $450,000!  Welcome to your dream haven at 1754 River Rd, Upper Black Eddy, PA. Experience the allure of living on the Delaware riverfront with this stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, now available at an irresistible new price of $450,000. This serene escape offers private shoreline access, ensuring breathtaking sunrises and pristine views of the New Jersey Bluffs.  Key Features: Home comes with a 2 year comprehensive AHS Home Warranty with coverage for major systems and appliances, roof leak repair, rekey service and more! Riverside Living: Boasting 100 feet of private shoreline with direct access to the D&L Trail, this property is perfect for water enthusiasts and nature lovers. Versatile Zoning: Unique VC (Village Center) Zoning allows for various commercial opportunities, adding to its investment potential. Effortless Entertaining: The home features an inviting layout with sunlight-drenched rooms, a cozy fireplace, and stunning hardwood floors. Luxurious Comfort: The primary bedroom offers scenic river views, and the spa-like main floor bathroom is recently renovated with high-end finishes. Additional Spaces: A finished basement for a home office, an attic for extra storage, and a 3-car detached garage. Outdoor Oasis: Enjoy the covered front porch, fenced backyard, wood deck, and a brick patio overlooking the Canal for an immersive outdoor experience. Convenient Location: Just 60 miles from NYC and Philadelphia, close to Lambertville, New Hope, and Milford, NJ.
